title: MusicNews | Christy Moore announces gigs at Dublin's Vicar Street and Bord Gais Energy Theatre
text:
Christy Moore has announced several gigs at both Vicar Street and the Bord Gais Energy Theatre in Dublin next year.
The folk titan will play his spiritual home of Vicar Street on April 13th and 14th , and the larger Bord Gais Energy Theatre on Friday, May 6th.
Tickets for all gigs are €39.50, €45.00 and €49.50 and on sale next Thursday, October 22nd at 9am from usual outlets.
